Ay, ay, ay.

620
00:34:06,901 --> 00:34:08,520
Ya, ya, ya, ya.

621
00:34:09,860 --> 00:34:12,440
No, no, no, no, no.

622
00:34:12,441 --> 00:34:13,240
Ya, ya, ya, ya.

623
00:34:13,241 --> 00:34:13,680
